tags.name:
lrn-gitgraph
For each branch in your repo use the following git command:
```
git log [branch_name] --format='{"refs": "%d", "commit": "%h", "tree": "%t", "parent": "%p", "subject": "%s", "date": "%cd", "author": "%an %ae"},' --reverse
```
